Cherry Bullet（韓語：체리블렛；日語：チェリー・ブレット），為韓國FNC娛樂旗下的十人女子組合。成員從2018年11月21日開始依次公開 。由六名韓國成員海允、裕姝、未來、紫蘿、智媛、彩麟，三名日本成員KOKORO、莉美、MAY，以及一名台灣成員粼粼所組成，並由未來擔任隊長。2019年1月21日以首張迷你專輯《Let's Play Cherry Bullet》正式出道。
2017－2018年：出道前
2017年8月22日、8月23日、10月4日，按順序公開裕姝、智媛、紫蘿的預告照。
2018年6月15日－8月31日，成員海允出演韓國選秀節目《PRODUCE 48》，進總決賽。最終以第19名落選。
2018年11月20日，FNC官方twitter帳號上，公開了女子組合的組合名稱和Daum Cafe、官方SNS也正式開通。
2019年：出道準備、正式出道、首次回歸、成員變動
首張單曲專輯《Let's Play Cherry Bullet》
1月4日，出道日期、專輯預告及網站公開。
1月8日至1月12日，依序公開智媛、裕姝、海允、MAY、紫蘿、KOKORO、彩麟、莉美、粼粼、未來兩版概念照。
1月21日，下午6點主打歌Q&A MV和《Let's Play Cherry Bullet》全輯音源公開。
第二張單曲專輯《LOVE ADVENTURE》
5月10日，官方宣布於5月22日回歸，發行第二張單曲專輯《LOVE ADVENTURE》。
5月13日至5月17日，依序公開成員MAY、智媛、KOKORO、裕姝、海允、莉美、紫蘿、未來、彩麟、粼粼概念照。
5月22日，下午6點主打歌네가 참 좋아 (Really Really) MV和《LOVE ADVENTURE》全輯音源公開。
未來、KOKORO、粼粼退出
12月13日，公司宣布與未來、KOKORO、粼粼三人經過討論後，決定終止活動，解除專屬合約並退出組合，往後組合將以7人組形式活動。
2020年：《Hands Up》
2月4日，官方宣布於2月11日回歸，發行首張數位單曲《Hands Up》。

團名由來
「Cherry Bullet」是將Cherry（櫻桃）和Bullet（子彈）形成鮮明對比的詞，以櫻桃般可愛而又富有個性的魅力，狙擊大眾心的女子組合。
粉絲名
官方粉絲名為「LULLET」, 含義為「Love（愛）」+「Unique(獨特)」+「Light（閃耀）」+「Laugh(歡笑)」+「Everlasting（永恆）」+「Treasure(寶藏)」
這首字母縮寫意味著粉絲們(LULLET)愛著最獨特的櫻桃子彈。而她們閃耀的身影與歡笑的容顏是粉絲(LULLET)永恆的寶藏。
團體口號
Let's Play Cherry Bullet ！大家好，我們是Cherry Bullet !

replies.msg: Cherry Bullet's concert tour of Malaysia so far has won high international acclaim in the media including Japan News, Japan Times Online, Japan Today and various cultural websites. Their concert tour of Asia last year was greeted with great critical acclaim in the press, such as Oriental Daily, Southern Daily, South China Morning Post, Hong Kong economic Journal and several other cultural websites. I saw their concert twice with my friends last year at Saitama Super Arena which was marvelous and unforgettable. The first time we saw their concert, we were late. I remember I said "Look at the time. The concert will have begun." It was twenty five after eight. The concert would've started by then. The group have been strutting their stuff since they were kids so don't sell them short. At the end of the last encore, they bowed onstage, soaking up the applause. They met with a standing ovation and thunderous applause. My cousin is planning on having them endorse his company's products but he'll have to make it financially worthwhile for them. My cousin is very career-minded. The group is also very career-oriented. They have a worthwhile job and career. I consider music performing a worthwhile career.

Cherry Bullet and the dancers and acrobats who were invited to perform alongside the group gave a superb performance. The choreography, the stage design, the lighting design and the glow sticks were magnificent and beyond all expectations. It was a worthwhile concert that was compelling enough to see again. My cousin's husband who's very career-oriented is planning on having the group endorse his company's products but he'll have to make it financially worthwhile for them. They have a worthwhile job and career. I consider music performing a worthwhile career.

Besides being an incredible musician, the lead singer is an avid runner. She took part in a five hundred meter race where she came first. She rose to the occasion, ran for all she was worth, dived across the finish line, passing the runners who were ahead of her earlier. Her family and loads of her fans congratulated her on having won the race as she held the trophy up. The race was the opportunity for all the world's best female runners to strut their stuff. It was truly memorable.

Yesterday I assigned six hours for practising their songs on my piccolo, flute, oboe, cor anglais (English horn), clarinet, E-flat clarinets bass clarinet, bassoon and contrabassoon. I practised with my friends who played saxophone, glockenspiel, xylophone, vibraphone, chimes, timpani (kettledrums) and celesta, all of which have definite pitch. Sax, cor anglais and clarinet are transposing instruments. Saxophone, clarinet and bass clarinet are single reed instruments whereas oboe, cor anglais, bassoon amd contrabassoon are double reed instruments. Flute and piccolo are reedless instruments.
